{
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"会话生命周期：\n1. init —— 创建会话，绑定 harness 和工作目录\n2. run/ask —— 在会话中发送消息，AI 记住上下文\n3. fork —— 从当前会话分叉新会话（保留历史但独立演进）\n4. summary —— 查看会话摘要\n使用 --session 参数可以在 request 中复用会话上下文\n"
,
"en"
:
"Session lifecycle:\n1. init —— Create session with harness and workspace\n2. run/ask —— Send messages with context memory\n3. fork —— Branch new session from current (preserves history)\n4. summary —— View session summary\nUse --session in request to reuse session context\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session <subcmd> [options]"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent session init --harness claude"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 创建新会话，绑定 claude"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Create new session with claude"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent session run --id <session-id> \"Fix the authentication bug\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 在已有会话中执行请求（保留上下文）"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Run in existing session (preserves context)"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent session ask --id <session-id> \"Should I use JWT or session cookies?\""
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 交互式提问，AI 基于历史上下文回答"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Ask question with historical context"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent session fork --id <session-id>"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 分叉会话，尝试不同方案"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Fork session to try alternative approach"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent session ls"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 列出所有会话"
,
"en"
:
"Example: List all sessions"
}
]
,
"init"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"创建新的 AI 会话，可绑定 harness 和工作目录"
,
"en"
:
"Create new AI session, optionally bind harness and workspace"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session init [options]"
]
,
"--harness"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"指定 AI 工具接口"
,
"en"
:
"Specify AI tool interface"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://agent/data/harness.jso"
}
}
,
"--workspace"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"绑定工作目录，会话中的 AI 可以访问该目录"
,
"en"
:
"Bind working directory accessible by AI during session"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__dir"
}
}
}
,
"run"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"在已有会话中发送请求（保留完整对话历史）"
,
"en"
:
"Send request in existing session (preserves full conversation history)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session run --id <session-id> <prompt>"
]
,
"-i|--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"会话 ID（从 session init 或 session ls 获取）"
,
"en"
:
"Session ID (from session init or session ls)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format"
}
}
}
,
"--harness"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"临时切换 AI 工具（仅本次请求生效）"
,
"en"
:
"Temporarily switch AI tool (only for this request)"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://agent/data/harness.jso"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"提示词内容"
,
"en"
:
"Prompt content"
}
}
}
,
"ask"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"在会话中提问（支持 --yes-no 限制 AI 只回答 YES/NO）"
,
"en"
:
"Ask question in session (supports --yes-no for YES/NO-only answers)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session ask --id <session-id> <question>"
]
,
"-i|--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"会话 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Session ID"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format"
}
}
}
,
"--yes-no"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"限制 AI 仅回答 YES 或 NO"
,
"en"
:
"Restrict AI to answer YES or NO only"
}
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"问题内容"
,
"en"
:
"Question content"
}
}
}
,
"summary"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看会话摘要（历史消息数、当前状态等）"
,
"en"
:
"View session summary (message count, current status, etc.)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session summary --id <session-id>"
]
,
"-i|--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"会话 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Session ID"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format"
}
}
}
}
,
"fork"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"从已有会话分叉新会话（保留历史，独立演进）"
,
"en"
:
"Fork new session from existing one (preserves history, independent evolution)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session fork --id <session-id>"
]
,
"-i|--id"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"要分叉的源会话 ID"
,
"en"
:
"Source session ID to fork from"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"UUID 格式"
,
"en"
:
"UUID format"
}
}
}
}
,
"ls"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"列出所有会话（支持 CSV/TSV 格式导出）"
,
"en"
:
"List all sessions (supports CSV/TSV export)"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent session ls [options]"
]
,
"--csv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"CSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"CSV format output"
}
}
,
"--tsv"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"TSV 格式输出"
,
"en"
:
"TSV format output"
}
}
}
}

